      "value": "<p><strong>Beast Mask (Fetish)</strong></p><p><em>Creation Cost: 8 Gnosis.</em></p><p><strong>Effect:</strong></p><p>As an action, transform into the animal represented by the mask.</p><ul><li>Use the beast's stat block (CR 1 or lower)</li><li>Retain Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma</li><li>You cannot use Garou features or regenerate while transformed</li></ul><p>Lasts for 1 hour.</p><p><strong>Fetish Rating:</strong> 3. <strong>Minimum Max Gnosis:</strong> 7. Cannot use while raging unless this fetish states otherwise. Spirit Attention: you can have a number of actively empowered fetishes equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1); instantaneous effects do not count after resolution.</p><p><code>[GAROU_FETISH] id=beast-mask; rating=3; minGnosis=7; activation=action</code></p>",
